<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>      
<h1>LED Dance Platform Mode Interface</h1>
<h3>Check one box then submit to change the mode of the LED Dance Platform.</h3>
<h5>Each one shows the mode as it is specified in the software, and a description of each.<h6>
<form>
<input type="radio" name="mode" value="randsquares" checked>Random squares not changing<br><br>

<input type="radio" name="mode" value="randsquares change=True">Random squares that change to music<br><br>

<input type="radio" name="mode" value="randsquares halfblack=True">Half black squares half random squares<br><br>

<input type="radio" name="mode" value="randsquares change=True,halfblack=True">Half black squares half random squares that change to the music<br><br>

<input type="radio" name="mode" value="bassring">"bassring": Random squares that change to music with a ring on edge that changes to bass<br><br>

<input type="radio" name="mode" value="visualize1">"visualize1": Visualizer that emanates out from the center<br><br>

<input type="radio" name="mode" value="levels">"levels": Power levels of different ranges in the music<br><br>

<input type="radio" name="mode" value="thetachi">"thetachi": Displays Theta then a Chi to the bass of the music<br><br>

<input type="radio" name="mode" value="solidcolor">Displays solid RGB color on platform (Lookup the values if you don't know)<br>

R:<input type="text" name="red" value=0-255>G:<input type="text" name="g" value=0-255>B:<input type="text" name="b" value=0-255><br><br>

<input type="radio" name="mode" value="textdisplay">Check this to display text you type into the input space<br>
Display:<input type="text" name="text"><br><br><br><br>
<input type=submit value="Change Mode">
</form> 
</html>
